  <brief_title>Trial Assessing Evolocumab(AMG145) Compared to LDL-C Apheresis in Subjects Receiving LDL-C Apheresis Prior to Study Enrollment</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Actively Controlled, Open-label, Multicenter Study of Efficacy and Safety of Evolocumab Compared With Low Density Lipoprotein Cholesterol (LDL-C) Apheresis, Followed by Single-Arm Evolocumab Administration in Subjects Receiving LDL-C Apheresis Prior to Study Enrollment</official_title>
