  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the efficacy of subcutaneous (SC) evolocumab, compared to regularly scheduled
      low density lipoprotein cholesterol (LDL-C) apheresis, on reducing the need for future
      apheresis
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
